** '''[[Yale]]''': 
* '''[[Cantonese]]'''
** '''[[Jyutping]]''':
** '''[[Penkyamp]]''': 
** '''[[Yale]]''': gu2kam4

===Noun===
#{{musici}} [[guqin]]; Chinese seven-stringed zither
#:*[[彈]]古琴 (play the ''guqin'')
#(''place'') '''Guqin Tai''' 《古琴[[臺]]》 (Guqin Terrace or Heptachord Terrace, etc.); the name of a place in [[Wuhan]], [[China]]

====Usage notes====
*In the past, the 古琴 was referred to only as 琴, but it has the prefix 古- to distinguish it from other instruments which also use the word 琴. It can be referred to as 琴 after 古琴 is used in the first instance.
*It is sometimes confused with the [[guzheng]] ([[古筝]]) which is a different stringed instrument.

